01:00:12.810 --> 01:00:14.355 align:middle line:90%
There's a lot of energy around.

01:00:14.355 --> 01:00:15.730 align:middle line:84%
So it frequently
happens that you

01:00:15.730 --> 01:00:20.210 align:middle line:84%
can write a product or a
