01:00:24.170 --> 01:00:27.490 align:middle line:84%
in many ways, then you
could get a clean estimate

01:00:27.490 --> 01:00:31.050 align:middle line:90%
for the size of the product set.

01:00:31.050 --> 01:00:36.950 align:middle line:84%
By playing around with the sort
of products that you consider

01:00:36.950 --> 01:00:40.020 align:middle line:84%
and by some experience
and craft and skill,

01:00:40.020 --> 01:00:41.460 align:middle line:90%
we can get that to happen.

01:00:41.460 --> 01:00:45.240 align:middle line:90%


01:00:45.240 --> 01:00:49.480 align:middle line:84%
OK, so this is the analog
