01:00:58.040 --> 01:00:59.980 align:middle line:90%
to fit into this thing.

01:00:59.980 --> 01:01:04.960 align:middle line:90%


01:01:04.960 --> 01:01:08.560 align:middle line:84%
So this Q is the
